<h1 id="ðŸ“–-expanded-cheat-sheet" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#ðŸ“–-expanded-cheat-sheet"><span>ðŸ“– Expanded Cheat Sheet</span></a></h1>
<ul>
<li>Readme extracted from <a href="https://gist.github.com/bradtraversy/c831baaad44343cc945e76c2e30927b3" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">BradTraversy<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></li>
